## 11. Suggested Swagger Demo Flow

Use this flow for testing or presentation:

```txt
1. Call GET /users before login
   Expected: 401 Unauthorized

2. Call POST /user with valid data
   Expected: 201 Created

3. Call POST /auth/login with valid credentials
   Expected: 200 OK and authentication cookie is set

4. Call GET /auth/me
   Expected: current authenticated user

5. Call GET /users again
   Expected: 200 OK with safe user list

6. Call POST /auth/logout
   Expected: Logout successful

7. Call GET /auth/me again
   Expected: 401 Unauthorized
```

